{"tid":389134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(劉鑾雄有心有力)  甘比認懷孕4個月","createTime":"2017-09-06T03:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T08:07:01.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9991ba6c65878d78e5e5274adfc3ba5917196947","tid":389134,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57172200&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57172200%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170906&d=E2yCoEQOH8xopYD9uxQ%2FptibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=4160813e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57172200%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170906&h=604fe84a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57172200&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170906</a><br />\n<br />\n【獨家】劉太甘比認懷孕4個月 凸肚行街保鑣高度戒備<br />\n<br />\n即時娛樂  2017-09-06 00:02:46 HKT\t<br />\n<br />\n恭喜！恭喜！城中66歲富豪劉鑾雄（大劉）果然有心有力，病癒後冇耐再有好消息！37歲嘅甘比（陳凱韻）又有咗喇！真係咪話唔勁呀！雖然甘比同大劉已經育有一仔一女，不過今胎意義唔同，家姐秀樺、細佬仲學出生時，大劉同甘比仍然係男女朋友嘅關係，而今胎就係佢地正式結婚後生嘅第一胎，當然會更加開心啦！<br />\n<br />\n早前大劉多次分身家，令外間懷疑大劉健康有問題，o依家劉太甘比再大肚有咗近4個月，足已證明大劉身體已經冇乜大礙，仍然有心有力。雖然粗身大細，不過甘比都不忘shopping當做運動，日前約下午5時許，《蘋果》仲見佢一個人出現喺銅鑼灣利園商場嘅Herm&egrave;s專門店買嘢，見佢著住一條鬆身牛仔裙，步伐輕盈咁喺店入面行咗一圈睇手袋，店員見到劉太，當然要招呼貴賓啦，見甘比拎住手機放大咗張相俾店員睇，店員搖搖手，估計店裡冇甘比想要嘅款式，後來疑似係店舖經理嘅職員出埋嚟招呼劉太，見佢同嗰位經理有講有笑，睇嚟佢同店員們都非常熟落。<br />\n<br />\n逗留咗唔夠半粒鐘已經離開，甘比身邊保鑣見有記者影相都好緊張，即刻擋喺前面開路，不過甘比走出店時，風一吹好明顯肚凸凸，身形發福咗唔少，似乎真係有咗身孕，《蘋果》打畀甘比恭賀！甘比就表示：「多謝晒！」問到佢有咗幾多個月？佢就話：「其他嘢唔回應啦！多謝關心！」"},{"pid":"b7c4c26b79f5414a5c9e527b19b1f3afce24a21a","tid":389134,"uid":27447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce4d6e0dd8b99a1a4dd6fe2514e424423d0e2a5","tid":389134,"uid":135717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3908d7618dc8fe219927c041e10fff7c9e80c528","tid":389134,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d946744655a0f5dbe8396a912de72e55ffe53985","tid":389134,"uid":39177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"一定係女上男下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a82534ac24080bade8335d59da063801aca1e4","tid":389134,"uid":12565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽乜唔妥<br />\n恭喜晒</span>"},{"pid":"7ad69cc796aefa39b9f75026435387bdef32fbf6","tid":389134,"uid":109602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b2b065c8b8a16743f353a96fe4b061d9b1c247d","tid":389134,"uid":73613,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37d331f1a86b221ae4145ec6392586209a1f0eca","tid":389134,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:37:07.000Z","msg":"搬去娛樂台啦, 關人撚事咩"},{"pid":"a2882da89de8556109ff9a059914d65c8ffac087","tid":389134,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"究竟個肚入面係大劉個仔定係個孫呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef7476fbc7a6cbe613f2ab257b36319b8ac2fba","tid":389134,"uid":118596,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:26:43.000Z","msg":"有位老人去醫院做健康檢查，<br />\n<br />\n檢查過程中，老人不斷向醫生炫耀自己的新婚妻子<br />\n<br />\n老人：「我那新婚妻子啊，臉蛋嫩，皮膚又好，身材更是一級棒！」<br />\n<br />\n醫生：「嗯.. 是嗎」<br />\n<br />\n老人：「是啊！他才25歲，我們新婚三個月，他就黏我黏得不得了囉！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生：「....」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老人繼續說：「你猜怎麼來著？她懷孕了！我讓她懷孕了！厲害吧！！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生：「你讓我想起一個老朋友，他是個獵人，有次他去非洲打獵，<br />\n<br />\n　　　　臨面的是一隻兇猛的大獅子，他拿起背後的獵槍準備瞄準，<br />\n　　　　沒想到帶錯東西，拿成雨傘了，他靈機一動，<br />\n<br />\n　　　　拿起雨傘自己配音 『砰』了三聲，沒想到獅子居然倒地而死！！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老人：「那怎麼可能嘛！一定是別人幹的！！」<br />\n<br />\n醫生：「我也是這麼想的。」"},{"pid":"6a4b8c6b35a36ea5bcc15ef3eafae7cdd16b25bd","tid":389134,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"遺產點分先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ddd0e13bb6e686b2e5c61982e7b36e2ac02601","tid":389134,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:28:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d6a00d77e66cdfae40dcdf917e85d1e6fb75d4e","tid":389134,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:29:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇打獵獅子故事</blockquote><br />\n「我也是這麼想的」"},{"pid":"9deb8520ff3e291ad2d8c99847c17baa0682afcc","tid":389134,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20160106/large/06ec2p14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160106%2Flarge%2F06ec2p14.jpg&h=9617fc73&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夫..日..."},{"pid":"377cb52ceee196e810f0076375f2f9e8da0e16ea","tid":389134,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有位老人去醫院做健康檢查，<br />\n<br />\n檢查過程中，老人不斷向醫生炫耀自己的新婚妻子<br />\n<br />\n老人：「我那新婚妻子啊，臉蛋嫩，皮膚又好，身材更是一級棒！」<br />\n<br />\n醫生：「嗯.. 是嗎」<br />\n<br />\n老人：「是啊！他才25歲，我們新婚三個月，他就黏我黏得不得了囉！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生：「....」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老人繼續說：「你猜怎麼來著？她懷孕了！我讓她懷孕了！厲害吧！！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫